{"title":"Mareo_Urgencias","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología/Mareo_Urgencias.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Mareo en\\NUrgencias","guid":"ndS_HUoqR4unGPr6odO8ew","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación por\\NPerfil Temporal","guid":"p7ziGDTuRgSEZ5t2IyTwCw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"SÍNDROME\\NVESTIBULAR AGUDO\\N(SVA)","guid":"y4hYYzFgRXWb72VMyBLFyw","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Definición → vértigo continuo >24h + nistagmo + inestabilidad","guid":"5vFUeC6gTc2LjX2EIrjx-Q","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial\\NPRINCIPAL","guid":"7qn6lhdyQJGxE7phVVbqVw","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Neuronitis vestibular (periférico)","guid":"DtCpOa-VSiKkWv-jsGCW0g","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"ACV de fosa posterior (central) → AICA, PICA, cerebeloso","guid":"svJ3ArtRSwGxF1MPOGMruQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"Evaluación → protocolo HINTS","guid":"tLYUsbEXSnWS4DYrP1ctuw","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"SÍNDROME VESTIBULAR\\NEPISÓDICO","guid":"pZbX95rUT6mzHwqSZMu3TQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Crisis Cortas\\N(segundos a minutos)","guid":"7r460kgQT42MzcD-jlRN0Q","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"VPPB → gatillado por movimientos cefálicos","guid":"97jmAAxcRyaGXFYqMjkbsw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Ortostatismo → frecuente en AM, sobremedicación antihipertensiva","guid":"hlxsGGOhTEeLMjYn-H4G4Q","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"Crisis de pánico → hiperventilación asociada","guid":"x1vy1u82TPG5Z6ZRwXWqoA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"TIA de fosa posterior → raro, descartar con factores de riesgo vascular","guid":"UFYK53NiS-2ExxvORgYsxw","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"9","text":"Paroxismia vestibular → compresión nervio vestibular en APC por AICA/arteria laberíntica","guid":"Hw5MWr_mQiuBM1ahd2qLAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"8","text":"Crisis Largas\\N(minutos a horas)","guid":"jTPJql9_T02hw-FFjtVGOw","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Enfermedad de Meniere → vértigo + hipoacusia + tinnitus + plenitud ótica","guid":"WVrZC8kSSISiahKMcMqkZA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Migraña vestibular → 50% asocia cefalea migrañosa,\\N20min-24h duración","guid":"Tx7HM0e3Rh6sRmR3ZGuT7w","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"GRAN IMITADORA → puede simular CUALQUIER síndrome vestibular","guid":"gV2-OSgBS9aM13kBQLPmCw","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Criterios Bárány Society/IHS","guid":"ODVze8XlQSSMDTPUgk_0UQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"1","text":"SÍNDROME\\NVESTIBULAR\\NCRÓNICO","guid":"QZqhTcz_QcSxx4a_LlAcZw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Vestibulopatía\\Nbilateral","guid":"fwlQEba6QgGSem-dI4ocCg","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Presbivestibulopatía (asociada a edad)","guid":"xDl34AE1TS-D-snVs5pVyg","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Ototóxicos → ATB aminoglucósidos, diuréticos, QMT (cisplatino)","guid":"thaeaKyAR7CJVjaT4ZSSGQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Idiopática","guid":"006DSojdSIWTPOuVGdEshQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"MPPP (Mareo Postural\\NPerceptual Persistente)","guid":"2Jh6vlhBTuGDgsN_WD09sA","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Personalidad ansiosa + episodio vestibular previo mal compensado","guid":"p75uzsF5Q4yqrkLS1dr8fA","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"Inestabilidad en bipedestación, NO en reposo","guid":"WPhcXr2cRDqNVrdEcG7uOQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"Requiere rehabilitación kinesiológica","guid":"-qH1QvhnRLKkqB21ko2sXA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"1","text":"SÍNDROME\\NVESTIBULAR\\NGATILLADO","guid":"ua4ukEcyQfGWMLm8lOGizg","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"VPPB canal posterior → Dix-Hallpike","guid":"MLyO-ZFzSB6GlvCb0CZEcA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"VPPB canal lateral → McClure/Roll Test","guid":"CxQt-axRR2yBu-yaf46toQ","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"Síndrome de 3ra ventana →\\Ngatillado por ruido/Valsalva","guid":"qCQmiR1-SpyLkai8c_qPog","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Dehiscencia canal semicircular superior (más frecuente hoy)","guid":"TKZ8xJz3RSW0qE3y7K_D2g","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"OMC colesteatomatosa","guid":"rOwDcSNQTOio3UL9ZDryAA","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Sífilis terciaria (histórico)","guid":"CzEmE8mNT_CSzJw1H9AAig","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"0","text":"Mareo Inespecífico\\N(Undifferentiated Dizziness)","guid":"VvTTLBTuR_eR5z8bi4g-cQ","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Definición → sensación vaga de inestabilidad/aturdimiento SIN vértigo verdadero","guid":"Jy8Xz0IRRXy6MELFM-WUnQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Prevalencia → hasta 20-30% de consultas por mareo en urgencias","guid":"di1tu9LjTQeCxY4H2ES14g","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"NO ES diagnóstico final → requiere evaluación dirigida","guid":"mrzx1YtkShOA1mjK8DBVMg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"Categorías\\Ndiagnósticas a\\Ndescartar","guid":"hU_bNUgQQuKscyv1AriAsA","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Presíncope /\\Nhipoperfusión\\Ncerebral","guid":"yMaU247WSVOJ53qflAsPKg","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Hipotensión ortostática → ortostatismo positivo (caída PAS >=20 o PAD >=10 mmHg)","guid":"P9BX02PEQeSz_CoIO25EaA","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Arritmias → bradicardia, taquicardia, FA paroxística","guid":"5p3mP7y3RMiFLiHG4TisQg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Estenosis aórtica severa → soplo sistólico eyectivo, síncope esfuerzo","guid":"WksHtQ_eRZaHqp5fRvk_7Q","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"Hipovolemia → deshidratación, sangrado oculto (GI, aneurisma)","guid":"Aav7IizBQLiWclt3T6--3Q","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"41","text":"Síncope vasovagal → pródromos vegetativos","guid":"l6vRfs4bRw69vIISHUvxrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"40","text":"Causas\\Nmetabólicas","guid":"y0Rn77XfRGiatsjRoFkdTA","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"Hipoglicemia → revisar en TODO paciente diabético","guid":"Ga_L-W7qROG7T9Kaw41c4Q","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"Anemia severa → Hb <7 g/dL o crónica compensada","guid":"P4yc2RXbQhuUkCtxWyuFZQ","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"Alteraciones electrolíticas → hiponatremia, hipocalcemia","guid":"T7Ytb0q6Rj6dJuwIeLhk4Q","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"Hipotiroidismo / hipertiroidismo","guid":"x7McP_LOTn-J--9QeuJP_Q","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"Hipoxia / hipercapnia → especialmente EPOC, SAHOS","guid":"QZ3vXQz_SFO8RAVP_MHEoA","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"40","text":"Causas farmacológicas\\N(MUY frecuente en AM)","guid":"B4IHrgerRVe9tykastIv2Q","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Antihipertensivos → IECA, ARA II, diuréticos, betabloqueadores","guid":"v9_NkvJRQ62VES606lmJcA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Benzodiazepinas → sedación, ataxia","guid":"Dt3dABQ4THiyqR3yUru5sg","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"Opioides → mareo dosis-dependiente","guid":"e43ZKmkxSFa61UJ633-1IA","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"53","text":"Antiepilépticos → carbamazepina, fenitoína, pregabalina","guid":"W0s26n7iSsaudxqKSs_V7w","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"53","text":"Anticolinérgicos → carga anticolinérgica acumulada","guid":"8S4ggEdXTkiRiNuykEpMUA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"53","text":"Antidepresivos → ISRS (inicio o suspensión), tricíclicos","guid":"aOiuWQSLTqSNeNIYZomh2w","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"53","text":"Alfa-bloqueadores → tamsulosina (ortostatismo)","guid":"QcnXfLmMTLCXoGBHspsM1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"40","text":"Causas psiquiátricas/\\Nfuncionales","guid":"Sk7cmXKFQvyzK2YSii64Gw","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Trastorno de ansiedad generalizada","guid":"uqslobR-TPOd84Rg-u3Mtw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Trastorno de pánico → hiperventilación, parestesias, opresión torácica","guid":"VFjJIrPgQUa9DpxA0dMKng","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"MPPP (Mareo Postural Perceptual Persistente) → funcional/psicógeno","guid":"L9DjJ1Y6SPSrqqmcH0jVLA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"Depresión → mareo como somatización","guid":"5OWczLZPSA2JNqwWIMBUVA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"61","text":"Simulación (raro pero considerar en contexto médico-legal)","guid":"FBHmDm1yRvCsa5BJ0QA3mQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"40","text":"Causas neurológicas\\Nno vestibulares","guid":"Ghn7K8HEQEWoA5uZ6VfJgA","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Neuropatía periférica → pérdida proprioceptiva","guid":"qJgV5zbsRPaCbZHN-b0gVQ","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Enfermedad de Parkinson → inestabilidad postural","guid":"SK7aowiZQseueMjyoc64rQ","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Hidrocefalia normotensiva → tríada de Hakim (marcha, cognición, incontinencia)","guid":"UbgKsh0QRqGXYHDTrSZdvQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"Estenosis cervical → mielopatía cervical con inestabilidad","guid":"ghq7KHwWRCa0TAJatJwDJg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"36","text":"Evaluación mínima\\Nrecomendada en\\Nurgencias","guid":"vuuYepsITNuHaaXXafKQJA","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Anamnesis dirigida → temporalidad, gatillantes, fármacos, comorbilidades","guid":"WWGw0sKsS-6Jxzx-tLWJTA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Signos vitales con ORTOSTATISMO → acostado y de pie (3 min)","guid":"Q9ILWloFSQCwjNy9SlfAow","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"Examen neurológico focalizado → pares craneanos, cerebelo, marcha","guid":"EWJraLhwQdCccaFsoo-uwQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"Evaluación auditiva básica → frote de dedos bilateral","guid":"Hil81GJRTgKB7O8gu8eF4w","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"Glicemia capilar → rápida, económica, descarta hipoglicemia","guid":"TLQrAYiPQo29yWqjMf-pBw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"72","text":"Hemograma + electrolitos → si sospecha metabólica","guid":"7atVM87CRn62tYTCqbpUZw","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"72","text":"ECG → descartar arritmia, BAV, QTc prolongado","guid":"q4eckDKPSjqjP-BOPOlS9w","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"72","text":"Si focalidad neurológica → neuroimagen urgente","guid":"w3NjlF-HTxW3hUOki0jXJg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"Protocolo HINTS\\N(Head Impulse,\\NNystagmus, Test of\\NSkew)","guid":"lBRMc-yMR1y0_zCVM6ShKw","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"INDICACIÓN → solo en SVA con nistagmo espontáneo presente","guid":"HVYSRe6vRwSIhJmpuhULZQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Componente 1 →\\NHEAD IMPULSE TEST\\N(HIT)","guid":"lourmAR0Tr2eghqgcMv8rQ","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Normal (sin sacada correctiva) → CENTRAL hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"IM075q9sRXKRmmm1Su60yg","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"Anormal (sacada correctiva presente) → sugiere PERIFÉRICO","guid":"GJj5JwIjRx2GzJVAEhTk2w","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"Sensibilidad aislada 76.8% (IC 95% 64.4-85.8%)","guid":"hsdbv6DZT6WB8X96BJkTqg","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"83","text":"Especificidad aislada 89.1% (IC 95% 75.8-95.6%)","guid":"y2vF418lQ52Uq0IphzoqYg","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"81","text":"Componente 2 →\\NTIPO DE\\NNISTAGMO","guid":"j97azhSKSOam47KyvnhxHQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"Unidireccional horizontal → sugiere periférico","guid":"KCDuDM6eRkCoJC6A912U_A","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"BIDIRECCIONAL → CENTRAL","guid":"IqwfzSNmTi6kVVlCGUp-mw","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"88","text":"VERTICAL puro (up-beat o down-beat) → CENTRAL","guid":"yyhx6F90QHSDisFhtCWotw","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"88","text":"TORSIONAL PURO en posición primaria → CENTRAL","guid":"f00heKfMRSe1I5p4myGlCg","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"88","text":"Desconjugado → CENTRAL","guid":"DO4figWNR4qVHS6hwOPhcg","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"88","text":"Sensibilidad nistagmo tipo central 50.7%, Especificidad 98.5%","guid":"CPap_8DQQiqjnDUQtCkpCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"81","text":"Componente 3 →\\NTEST OF SKEW\\N(Skew Deviation)","guid":"H8GryC2TTDykAHtdkVDZYw","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Desviación vertical al cover test alternante","guid":"jMow-JPrR_aT5zKIBW6YHg","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"ALTAMENTE ESPECÍFICO para patología central","guid":"whW85q-GTfGaW0syu-FgyQ","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"Sensibilidad 23.7% (baja) / Especificidad 97.6% (alta)","guid":"AnMKQ_iCR7OfkY96zuzWzA","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"81","text":"HINTS combinado →\\Nrendimiento diagnóstico","guid":"qT5_Q4hGRbOme1sUzX9V9A","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"Sensibilidad 92.9% (IC 95% 79.1-97.9%) → ALTA certeza","guid":"RvXYTVAQQGurmqzeZ30PPQ","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"Especificidad 83.4% (IC 95% 69.6-91.7%) → certeza MODERADA","guid":"aHD6MNwTSdClwOfqdFQ_qw","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"SUPERA a RM-DWI precoz (<24-48h) para ACV fosa posterior","guid":"aNXFlN60Qwm1OO8tXakb4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"81","text":"HINTS PLUS →\\Nagrega evaluación\\Nauditiva","guid":"Q6_Hk_C4RWWdc6xw_HRI5Q","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Frote de dedos bilateral → detectar hipoacusia aguda unilateral","guid":"paYuubT7QHmOr_YmhLSOrA","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"Hipoacusia aguda nueva → sospecha infarto arteria laberíntica/AICA","guid":"nKPIYdIcTUmsLDxrGEV_BQ","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"Sensibilidad 99.0% / Especificidad 84.8%","guid":"e0QjPNMBS6S86QdzrE-7Og","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"103","text":"VPP 100% para centralidad si HINTS central + hipoacusia","guid":"S6fGBrEbTiiTlX4C8nxFdg","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"81","text":"Evaluación\\Nauditiva adicional","guid":"8rYZWnX2T1SejPzjYYpzyw","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Sin antecedente de asimetría previa → hipoacusia nueva = imagen","guid":"hXh5e_G7QWSBaSlwdhcNIA","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Irrigación → arteria laberíntica (rama de AICA) → zona emergencia VIII par","guid":"x67BjPfdSza4vwG-tKpiMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"81","text":"Evaluación de MARCHA\\N(protocolo ampliado)","guid":"QG5HfauzSkynJBoT5NW0Hg","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"Inestabilidad grado 3 → imposibilidad de bipedestación sin ayuda o caídas francas","guid":"UBd_CctJQ2WEYEy6NX9WHw","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"VPP 100% para causa CENTRAL","guid":"IzU-4HbqSh2mmfNMvcrADg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"111","text":"Ataxia truncal/marcha → S 69.7%, E 83.7% (grados crecientes mayor S)","guid":"wFScQO85Rgmame99PWWsuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"81","text":"LIMITACIÓN\\NCRÍTICA","guid":"co8gWxLBSAiZvpNad8opfg","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"HINTS requiere entrenamiento específico","guid":"kqpZW3dPQieiiubdtrVThQ","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"Mayoría de urgenciólogos NO entrenados (GRACE-3, 2023)","guid":"-wmLvuY2TWqpgniR2BY70w","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"Sin entrenamiento → HINTS es INEXACTO","guid":"t4kMjNdRR62wbSgZeQOegw","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"115","text":"NO es estándar de cuidado legal actual en urgencias","guid":"3cp6CiFuTbm8kgUpvcVWcg","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"81","text":"Protocolo STANDING\\N(alternativa)","guid":"ys39m-eQRTanFYuY1_2ZYA","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"SponTAneous Nystagmus, Direction, Gait","guid":"y97x74kkSV677aAuUubZZA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"Combina nistagmo + inestabilidad de marcha + factores de riesgo vascular","guid":"de7rvYD8QISG6l8uAdhvng","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"Precisión diagnóstica comparable a HINTS+ cuando se entrena","guid":"ZgMJwFppSy6r-mH-ugKoaQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"0","text":"Maniobras Diagnósticas\\Nde VPPB","guid":"opVKsKjPQHW-qHriHC-_UQ","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"DIX-HALLPIKE\\N(canal posterior)","guid":"JLTXmaNqREGH8hkORZfX0A","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Técnica → rotación cefálica 45° + decúbito supino rápido","guid":"o3wnfA3iSaCRfrFzPxtpxQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"Positivo → nistagmo TORSIONAL con batida hacia ARRIBA","guid":"P9lYsQwDSFO0uycsE7KnMA","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"LATENCIA antes del inicio del nistagmo (segundos)","guid":"OM7LhlLQSZOd_V5EvoD0wA","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"INVERSIÓN del nistagmo al volver a posición sentada → CONFIRMA","guid":"SmjG7nwXTNKQpcMs8TpXyg","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"Sin inversión → sospechar causa central","guid":"fj5tqBO5RiK1fXFv4OqD5Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"124","text":"McCLURE / ROLL TEST\\N(canal lateral)","guid":"WX1pxqJKRH-06aS1g6DTJQ","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Técnica → cabeza 30° flexión + giro lateral","guid":"AXbVzvIwTBqVBrGiZYSR1Q","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Nistagmo GEOTRÓPICO → bate hacia el suelo en ambos lados","guid":"9j0aMkaoTe6eLXM_9r8Vbg","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"Variantes apogetrópicas existen","guid":"1u-FRmGrTQ-CcvkIo0IXUQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"0","text":"Neuroimagen","guid":"Rp3HPk3DRpCogwJdoH4qAg","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"TAC de cerebro →\\NDESACONSEJAR\\Nrutinariamente","guid":"EDXHm3iRSwO4YUqs9aYa0w","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"Sensibilidad MUY BAJA para ACV fosa posterior","guid":"-crCk0h4QJm5GI0C5MD0eg","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"NO aporta en SVA ni en episódico ni en gatillado","guid":"g3sSjMN5Qg6HglZDrUVYDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"135","text":"RM de fosa posterior →\\NESTÁNDAR si sospecha\\Ncentral","guid":"1T3Oowx2RR-C970e5BOonA","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Sensibilidad ~80% en agudo (<24-48h) → FALSOS NEGATIVOS posibles","guid":"K9sd7bkzSu6xbWu7IrFLLw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"Especificidad alta","guid":"7-NecG9sT6Ouv0gQMbl99w","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"Indicación → HINTS central o equívoco, sin examinador entrenado","guid":"mSsOhPanTDGsZXr7RRLaWg","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"GRACE-3 → si no hay examinador HINTS entrenado, RM como segunda opción","guid":"WvpwEeZ_SROCb-fi3WD_Ow","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"135","text":"Angio-TAC/Angio-RM\\Ncabeza y cuello","guid":"hRFgOJs_Qv60X5CyNFj62w","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"Indicación → sospecha TIA de fosa posterior","guid":"BwHyLk8fQKKmHOYLubEAyA","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"Síndrome episódico + factores de riesgo vascular","guid":"lI-WNLp-RWWEUI2fsb1Ovg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento\\Nen Urgencias","guid":"bzgtoSkZSAW1E9Jn9cmGIQ","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"NEURONITIS VESTIBULAR\\N(SVA periférico confirmado)","guid":"hCKdkDpETG6hLwZ9x812xw","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Corticoides → metilprednisolona/\\Nprednisona 1mg/kg/día (máx 60mg)","guid":"mgJ7pfJ-RQO6THmulWE_bA","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Iniciar si síntomas <3 DÍAS de evolución","guid":"VsSKSeV7RLCg1KtWihY07A","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"Beneficio en sintomatología aguda demostrado","guid":"a-a4LqmGQFy6T5mX9Rv4DQ","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":">3 días → sin beneficio en síntomas ni pronóstico a largo plazo","guid":"Ew9Hvi-nStejvjzaqs50rw","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"Sedantes vestibulares →\\Ndifenidol (antihistamínico)","guid":"SPByQfVtTliAjF0hsVoxmA","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"Uso CORTO plazo → no prolongar >48-72h (retrasa compensación)","guid":"xSWZvxFsTIaORbUcbjdRZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"148","text":"REHABILITACIÓN VESTIBULAR\\N→ iniciar ANTES de 3 días","guid":"JpwsivXLS-yoNP2ksw8AkQ","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Terapia del reflejo vestíbulo-ocular","guid":"EIopbEAGTxqMeginvcWxUA","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"Derivación precoz a tecnología médica/kinesiología","guid":"oogh9RyiRlePyd1VTpa55A","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"155","text":"MEJOR predictor de outcomes a largo plazo","guid":"hdZHEMIcQiG1E2ai2AsVrg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"147","text":"ENFERMEDAD DE MENIERE\\N(episódico)","guid":"gdIC4gaBRzmkXCISI82yiA","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Sedantes vestibulares → difenidol","guid":"KrGoJ3XlTMq5YvSQtcOByQ","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"Benzodiazepinas → uso puntual en crisis","guid":"w9WaBIF-TIidh4yraKox3A","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"Corticoides orales → considerar","guid":"qbeTXAUqSFS7aqINm3z49w","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"Corticoides transtimpánicos → evaluar en crisis agudas refractarias","guid":"b5axrtgUQOmosUTZWfEHKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"147","text":"VPPB","guid":"i0GQ3cIiQNyyQwwkF_2l0g","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"Maniobra de EPLEY (canal posterior) → tratamiento directo","guid":"X_YNzKm3SOuznkk75lQG1w","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"NO requiere imágenes","guid":"QEdzf8LgQiKhBCa_HPfTKg","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"Derivar a maniobras de reposición sin estudio previo","guid":"yKWt-UUQTmqn4STzUsOlbA","children":[]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"147","text":"MIGRAÑA\\NVESTIBULAR","guid":"4s0kPYNeQ8CaN9yvfmjHhQ","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"Puede simular los 3 tipos de síndromes vestibulares","guid":"KX3uLuyCTM2BewXPzmy2Sw","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"Sospecha → características de centralidad SIN inestabilidad severa + historia de migraña","guid":"tix1tw4DQA2d91kU0204zg","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"Ante duda → consultar a alguien más experimentado","guid":"sI77A_isQ8uzF-LQfNDAhA","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"Criterios de exclusión obligatorios antes de diagnosticar","guid":"DlHU-_qKT9-K3ZbJ2WbL7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"147","text":"MAREO INESPECÍFICO\\N→ manejo según etiología","guid":"zxtozRN-SJGm_YFG2U2kjw","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Ortostatismo → hidratación, ajuste fármacos, medias de compresión","guid":"YfqRvxJKQaGJsvQJ6LTO6w","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Hipoglicemia → corrección inmediata con glucosa oral/IV","guid":"1LLNRAJdT2-K6rYLYt31GQ","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"Arritmia → manejo específico, monitorización, cardio","guid":"ZTkbTCEHQpmauCCtDT42Fw","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"Anemia → transfusión si sintomática o Hb <7","guid":"uYPCJa-JRFqiiTIlqUlpvA","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"173","text":"Fármacos → suspender o ajustar causante (DEPRESCRIPCIÓN)","guid":"4CPtjupkRIql-S1LKV-hpQ","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"173","text":"Ansiedad/pánico → manejo no farmacológico, reasegurar, evitar BZD crónicas","guid":"Y4woXqFcQhi-liCIMGtHIQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas","guid":"GzxrJnUnSdSQ-WFgejsUrg","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"AM → mayor prevalencia de ortostatismo por polifarmacia antihipertensiva","guid":"ceADWP4oRqexOX_MBJLtoQ","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"Presbivestibulopatía → evaluación funcional integrada","guid":"N6XDsIu7ST6LTog7sXuW6g","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"Fragilidad → condiciona pronóstico post-SVA","guid":"R5FPO96mSpS-E-scxUDtxw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"MPPP → sarcopenia + problemas articulares agravan la inestabilidad","guid":"mCwVSRi7RNWvsgIKxJ1LLQ","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"180","text":"Corticoides en AM → monitorizar glicemia, considerar duración limitada","guid":"T3Ebp3F2QAGP3ZDj6NXI2A","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"180","text":"Rehabilitación vestibular precoz → CRUCIAL para evitar deterioro funcional","guid":"XsNCWpI-S9mZyQzCHMhBSQ","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"180","text":"Caídas → SVA/VPPB no tratado = factor precipitante de Fx cadera","guid":"id5vT3w4QXGvQ83VfSeMww","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"180","text":"Neuronitis mal compensada → riesgo de mareo crónico y aislamiento social","guid":"rg2fb3IrSIaXBYlN4NkH4Q","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"180","text":"Mareo inespecífico en AM → MULTICAUSAL (vestibular + ortostatismo + polifarmacia + sarcopenia)","guid":"hGwJ2WQ1S6SH_5heFQtYKg","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"180","text":"Deprescripción como intervención terapéutica → revisar STOPP/START","guid":"6uchtZM4SVqSm7sSEpQ_rg","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"180","text":"Evaluación multidimensional → VGI abreviada si mareo recurrente","guid":"Hr8PxYtYT92FKc-FFTWiAA","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"0","text":"Futuro y\\NTecnología","guid":"HQG50e_sT1-cahUENd4S-A","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"Tele-video-nistagmografía\\N(VNG remota)","guid":"bRNPsElHSZaeKxQC4HH-jg","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"Potencial para distinguir central vs periférico en urgencia","guid":"uLWQtuByRvqARxkRvqwCZg","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"Reduciría interconsultas innecesarias a neurología (~20% de IC por vértigo)","guid":"It0Lrzm_RZq0-LvEhS6OgA","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"IA aplicada a análisis de nistagmo → diagnóstico automatizado","guid":"Hxmu2AZTQLSxeUhzhgAcuA","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"192","text":"Entrenamiento en HINTS para urgenciólogos → prioridad educativa","guid":"6EBH_sn9TlOy4QLLvI3N3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"lXwXAaGDTj6Xvzf5brYPGw","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"HINTS solo es válido en SVA CON nistagmo espontáneo → NO usar en episódicos","guid":"cBxg7ZjsS_GcJXDq-ek6Sw","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"TAC de cerebro NO tiene rol en evaluación de vértigo agudo → preferir RM","guid":"XnM2A1SFQBi0rLJ-pFAPmg","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"HINTS+ SUPERA a RM-DWI precoz (<48h) en detección de ACV posterior","guid":"DXVMyri0TRaTrm0tP5lXLg","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"Nistagmo torsional puro en posición primaria = CENTRAL hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"ji9klUA7RL6a-nwxOsTfcA","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"198","text":"Inestabilidad grado 3 (caídas francas) = VPP 100% para causa central","guid":"rWj3adMUQ02C6xe_2VpGZg","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"198","text":"Migraña vestibular = gran imitadora → tenerla siempre en mente","guid":"wdfqBiTJRiG6DBqUBf32yA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"198","text":"Corticoides en neuronitis → solo útiles si <3 días de síntomas","guid":"58-Yy1dSR7KGh-4WzsjE-g","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"198","text":"Rehabilitación vestibular PRECOZ (<3 días) = mejor predictor de recuperación","guid":"PwUxkcxARJajatxeWPfhLQ","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"198","text":"En AM → descartar SIEMPRE ortostatismo por polifarmacia antes de asumir causa vestibular","guid":"AElyp1BmSgSFYThveNa_-w","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"198","text":"Mareo inespecífico NO es diagnóstico → buscar causa subyacente (presíncope, metabólica, fármacos)","guid":"avlDgRZRRF667E25Kr7jNw","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"198","text":"ECG + ortostatismo + glicemia = tríada mínima en mareo inespecífico del AM","guid":"k-MIJun2Tqeuv3K276hGQg","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"198","text":"DEPRESCRIBIR antes de agregar fármacos en mareo del adulto mayor","guid":"880mcxx-QlGXjLsqnXOzGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"3Jm6hmIAS1qUkuEG7a6w1A","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"1. Edlow JA et al. GRACE-3: Acute dizziness and vertigo in the ED. Acad Emerg Med. 2023;30(5):442-48.","guid":"ujUOXQdBQcmkY70aVhUH5g","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"2. Gottlieb M et al. HINTS for diagnosing central causes of AVS. Cochrane Database Syst Rev. 2023;11.","guid":"lhlj6APRSDemvZpGVyV_eA","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"3. Shah VP et al. Diagnostic accuracy of physical exam in ED patients with acute vertigo: meta-analysis.","guid":"-2sA7uDQQEeOvtJiqSjjow","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"4. Tarnutzer AA, Edlow JA. Bedside Testing in AVS - HINTS Plus and Beyond. Audiol Res. 2023;13(5):67.","guid":"999IEcKuSVm4_UgODHCFWQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"211","text":"5. Strupp M et al. AUVP/Vestibular neuritis: Diagnostic criteria. Bárány Society. J Vestib Res. 2022.","guid":"NoXxyXtJQB2MPVyca1vkfQ","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"211","text":"6. Lempert T et al. Vestibular migraine: Diagnostic criteria. J Vestib Res. 2012;22(4):167-172.","guid":"X5eI38IeRiS6gTmUGcFnVQ","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"211","text":"7. von Brevern M et al. BPPV: Diagnostic criteria. Bárány Society. J Vestib Res. 2015;25:105-117.","guid":"s6t32fzaQLyvLMi1r_b_JQ","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"211","text":"8. Lopez-Escamez JA et al. Diagnostic criteria for Meniere disease. Bárány Society. J Vestib Res. 2015.","guid":"JDgtK9_YTP6m1PZ67DWH2Q","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"211","text":"9. Kim HA et al. Hemodynamic orthostatic dizziness/vertigo: Diagnostic criteria. Bárány Society. 2019.","guid":"G1xKAfAERQGKMtdYPWiBzQ","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"211","text":"10. Jung I, Kim JS. Approach to dizziness in the ED. Clin Exp Emerg Med. 2015;2(2):75-88.","guid":"-jPGDWoZSMGNOa09EAqmTg","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"211","text":"11. Newman-Toker DE et al. TiTrATE: Novel approach to diagnosing acute dizziness and vertigo. Neurol Clin. 2015;33(3):577-599.","guid":"VAWLWgMEQGyH-1RzmPHGtQ","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":222,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"ORL","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología","filename":"Mareo_Urgencias","id":"map_1567","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Mareo_Urgencias"}